---

## Web Design

### LEA Professional
Website: https://www.leaprofessional.com

I built the LEA Professional website from the ground up for a new startup in the Pro AV space.
LEA was the first IoT-enabled professional amplifier, positioned as a "Smart Amp."

The goal of the website was to move away from the traditional corporate AV aesthetic
and instead create a modern, smart-tech visual language that clearly communicated
complex IoT value in an approachable way.

