## Social Media

### Influencer Collaborations
https://www.instagram.com/p/BrnmlNiAfXz/
https://www.instagram.com/p/Brnx053HnE7/

I worked directly with one of the industry's largest YouTube influencers to create
multiple pieces of content. This holiday-themed video featured the influencer playing
a Christmas song on one of our flagship products.

The objective was to leverage the influencer's existing audience to expand brand reach
and grow our own social media channels.

