## Campaigns

### Happy New Gear (Social Campaign)
https://www.instagram.com/p/Br0g955AQUU/

I planned and executed a user-generated content campaign encouraging customers to
submit photos of themselves with their newly purchased gear. Submissions were featured
throughout the Christmas season to spread holiday cheer while subtly promoting the brand.

---

### Happy New Gear (Landing Page)
https://www.sweetwater.com/happynewgear/

This is the campaign landing page where I wrote the copy and helped guide the overall
experience for the user-generated content initiative.

---

### Free LEA Professional Stickers
https://leaprofessional.com/send-a-sticker/

I created an evergreen free sticker campaign to collect leads and promote
user-generated content on social media.

This is the landing page that I designed and wrote copy for.

---

### Rock The Boat
https://www.instagram.com/p/Cejx9DOLTTm/

I was asked by the Michigan Maritime Museum in South Haven, MI to create a digital
marketing campaign for the first annual Rock The Boat event.

The campaign included:
- A 5-month social media strategy
- Design and creation of print and digital promotional materials
- Press release writing and local media outreach
- Digital event hosting and promotion on local websites

Production notes:
- Text and logo animation created in Adobe Premiere Pro
- Guitar track recorded in Logic Pro
- Audio synced to motion graphics with added stock crowd noise

